<!-- Session 1: Box Breathing - The Tactical Calm -->
<!-- Duration Target: 20 minutes -->
<!-- Speaking Rate: 0.85x (hypnotic pace) -->

<!-- Opening -->
<p>
<s>Welcome.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Find a comfortable position now.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>Whether you're sitting or lying down, allow your body to settle.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Let the weight of your body press gently into whatever supports you.</s>
</p>

<break time="2000ms"/>

<p>
<s>This is your time.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>The next twenty minutes belong entirely to you.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>There is nothing else you need to do.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Nowhere else you need to be.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Just here. Just now. Just breath.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<!-- Introduction to the Technique -->
<p>
<s>Today, you'll learn a breathing technique that has been used for thousands of years.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>Ancient yogis called it Sama Vritti, meaning equal fluctuation.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Modern practitioners call it Box Breathing.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Navy SEALs use it before entering combat.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Surgeons use it before operating.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>And now, you will use it to master your own nervous system.</s>
</p>

<break time="2000ms"/>

<p>
<s>The pattern is simple.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Four equal phases, like the four sides of a square.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>Inhale for four counts.</s>
<break time="600ms"/>
<s>Hold for four counts.</s>
<break time="600ms"/>
<s>Exhale for four counts.</s>
<break time="600ms"/>
<s>Hold for four counts.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>That's it. Simple in concept. Profound in effect.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<!-- Preparation -->
<p>
<s>Before we begin the practice, let's prepare your body.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>Place one hand on your belly.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Place the other hand on your chest.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>As you breathe, notice which hand moves first.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>In proper diaphragmatic breathing, the belly rises before the chest.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>The belly hand should move first and most.</s>
</p>

<break time="2000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Take a natural breath now, and observe.</s>
<break time="4000ms"/>
<s>Notice which hand rose first.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>There's no judgment here. Only observation.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Now, intentionally breathe into your belly.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Imagine your abdomen is a balloon, inflating with each inhale.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>Let the chest move only at the end of the breath.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Try it now. Inhale into the belly.</s>
<break time="5000ms"/>
<s>And release.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Good.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<!-- Round 1: Guided 4-4-4-4 -->
<p>
<s>Let's begin with three practice rounds.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>I'll guide you through each phase.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>There's no need to force anything.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Simply follow my voice, and let the breath find its own rhythm.</s>
</p>

<break time="2500ms"/>

<p>
<s>First round.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>When you're ready, begin to inhale.</s>
<break time="500ms"/>
<s>One.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Two.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Three.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Four.</s>
</p>

<break time="500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Now hold. Lungs gently full.</s>
<break time="500ms"/>
<s>One.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Two.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Three.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Four.</s>
</p>

<break time="500ms"/>

<p>
<s>And exhale. Slow and steady.</s>
<break time="500ms"/>
<s>One.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Two.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Three.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Four.</s>
</p>

<break time="500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Hold. Lungs empty. Soft and still.</s>
<break time="500ms"/>
<s>One.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Two.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Three.</s><break time="900ms"/>
<s>Four.</s>
</p>

<break time="1500ms"/>

<p>
<s>That's one complete cycle.</s>
<break time="1000ms"/>
<s>Notice how you feel.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Perhaps slightly calmer already.</s>
<break time="800ms"/>
<s>Perhaps not yet. Both are perfectly fine.</s>
</p>

